name: Not Different!
description:
NOT DIFFERENT!

An isometric puzzle game about a Human and AI trying to escape.

It has a short story and simple gameplay. There are 12 chapters in the game. It has a gameplay time of less than ten minutes. Game can be played with just a mouse.

I made the game Not Different during my first game jam.

I hope you enjoy the game and story I wrote. 

Good luck to everyone in jam.
